OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,FDonald Trump has extended the
OL,7,Fceasefire with Iran saying the Tehran
OL,8,Fregime was "seriously fractured".
OL,10,FThe last-minute move follows a request
OL,11,Ffrom Pakistan, which has been
OL,12,Fmediating in the conflict.
OL,14,FHowever, the US president said the
OL,15,Fblockade of Iran's ports would remain
OL,16,Fin force.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
