FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776819790
OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,FThe extension comes as the deadline
OL,7,Floomed on the current fragile truce
OL,8,Fand proposed talks in Islamabad were
OL,9,Fput on hold, amid tensions over the
OL,10,Fongoing stand-off in the Strait of
OL,11,FHormuz.
OL,13,FThe effective closure of the vital
OL,14,Fsupply route during the conflict has
OL,15,Finflicted a global economic shock and
OL,16,Fsent energy prices soaring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776819790
OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,FMeanwhile, military planners from
OL,7,Fcountries seeking to join a UK and
OL,8,FFrance-led defensive mission to keep
OL,9,Fthe waterway open once the Iran war
OL,10,Fends will meet in London on Wednesday.
OL,12,FFresh analysis published by the
OL,13,FResolution Foundation think tank also
OL,14,Fsuggested an escalation in the Middle
OL,15,FEast conflict could lead to a sharp
OL,16,Frise in UK Government borrowing, and
OL,17,Fslash most of the financial safety
OL,18,Fbuffer built up by Chancellor Rachel
OL,19,FReeves at last year's budget.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
