OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776819790
OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,FPakistan's leaders, including Prime
OL,7,FMinister Shehbaz Sharif, had made
OL,8,Ffrantic efforts on Tuesday to get both
OL,9,FWashington and Tehran to agree to
OL,10,Ffurther talks.
OL,12,FBut hopes faded as US vice president
OL,13,FJD Vance, expected to again lead US
OL,14,Fnegotiators, called off a trip to
OL,15,FPakistan as Iran refused to commit to
OL,16,Fattending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
