FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776819790
OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,FWriting in a post on his Truth Social
OL,7,Fplatform, Mr Trump said: "Based on the
OL,8,Ffact that the Government of Iran is
OL,9,Fseriously fractured, not unexpectedly
OL,10,Fso and, upon the request of Field
OL,11,FMarshal Asim Munir, and Prime Minister
OL,12,FShehbaz Sharif, of Pakistan, we have
OL,13,Fbeen asked to hold our Attack on the
OL,14,FCountry of Iran until such time as
OL,15,Ftheir leaders and representatives can
OL,16,Fcome up with a unified proposal.
OL,26,@oD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
