OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776819790
OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,F"I have therefore directed our
OL,7,FMilitary to continue the Blockade and,
OL,8,Fin all other respects, remain ready
OL,9,Fand able, and will therefore extend
OL,10,Fthe Ceasefire until such time as their
OL,11,Fproposal is submitted, and discussions
OL,12,Fare concluded, one way or the other."
OL,14,FOnly earlier, Mr Trump said he was
OL,15,Fready to renew attacks against Iran if
OL,16,Fprogress was not made.
OL,18,FThe president also told CNBC he did
OL,19,Fnot want to extend the ceasefire.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
