PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776819790
OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,FIn the event of a deal not being made
OL,7,Fsoon, Mr Trump said: "Well, I expect
OL,8,Fto be bombing because I think that's a
OL,9,Fbetter attitude to go in with.
OL,11,F"But, you know, we're ready to go. I
OL,12,Fmean, the military is raring to go."
OL,14,FHe argued Iran had no choice but to
OL,15,Fnegotiate.
OL,17,FMr Trump said: "We've taken out their
OL,18,Fnavy, we've taken out their air force,
OL,19,Fwe've taken out their leaders."
OL,26,@oD@VOUsD@AOUtD@dO]yD@POU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
