CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776819790
OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,FHe again claimed "regime change" and
OL,7,Fsaid those now in charge were "much
OL,8,Fmore rational".
OL,10,FBut Iran's parliamentary speaker,
OL,11,FMohammad Bagher Qalibaf, who had been
OL,12,Ftipped as Tehran's chief negotiator,
OL,13,Faccused the US president of seeking to
OL,14,Fturn the negotiating table into a
OL,15,F"table of surrender".
OL,17,F"We do not accept negotiations under
OL,18,Fthe shadow of threats," he wrote in an
OL,19,FX post, and said Iran was preparing
OL,20,F"to reveal new cards on the
OL,21,Fbattlefield".
OL,26,@nD@ROUnD@`O]oD@_OUpD@NO]wD@AOUwD@TO]yD@
