OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,FIn the UK, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer held talks with ministers and
OL,8,Fofficials on the Government's work to
OL,9,Fease pressures on the public caused by
OL,10,Fthe conflict.
OL,12,FThe Middle East Response Committee
OL,13,Fdiscussed ongoing contingency planning
OL,14,Fsuch as work with fuel suppliers,
OL,15,Fairlines and international
OL,16,Fcounterparts, a Government
OL,17,Fspokesperson said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
