OL,3,CTrump extends Iran ceasefire with
OL,4,CTehran regime 'seriously fractured'
OL,6,FThey also talked about diplomacy to
OL,7,Fsupport negotiations between the US
OL,8,Fand Iran, military planning as part of
OL,9,Fthe post-war mission to keep the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz open co-led with
OL,11,FFrance, and wider measures such as
OL,12,Fefforts to weaken the link between gas
OL,13,Fand electricity prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
